to be dumped
in landfills.

50:28.092 --> 50:33.397 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
John Shegerian is the CEO of
Electronics Recycling
International, the largest
e-waste recycling

50:33.497 --> 50:35.199 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
