50:35.299 --> 50:37.902 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JOHN SHEGERIAN, CEO, Electronics
Recycling
International: It takes hundreds
of employees

50:38.002 --> 50:41.672 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
