source of revenue
has plummeted.

50:50.080 --> 50:55.686 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JOHN SHEGERIAN: At the height of
the market,
when we would go to sell steel,
plastic, aluminum,

50:55.786 --> 51:03.193 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
