technology easy.

51:09.967 --> 51:14.371 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
KATIE CAMPBELL: Dell was the
first major computer
manufacturer to ban the export
of nonworking

51:14.471 --> 51:19.243 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
