recycling partners.

51:28.619 --> 51:32.656 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Dell says that more than 400
million pounds
of e-waste have been diverted
from U.S. landfills

51:32.756 --> 51:37.828 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
